      "side": 1,
      "message": "Just curious: there are many repetitive things in the comments (e.g., dstInfo description). Considering our tendency to reduce repetitions in code, is there a good way to reduce such repetitions in comments so we don\u0027t have to modify multiple places for a single change in the future?",
